text: Léonce Gaston Quentin was a French archer. He was born on 16 February 1880 and died on 1 December 1957. Quentin competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Léonce QuentinLéonce Gaston QUENTIN == References == Category:1880 births Category:1957 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for France Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France
